<Text: Antoinette Byron is an Australian actress best known for such television series as "Women in Prison", "Melrose Place", and for portraying the characters Skye Chandler on the soap opera "All My Children" and the role of Natalie Nash on the Australian soap opera "Home and Away", Byron was cast in the role of Nash and debuted in the 1999 season premiere.>
